<body>
    <h1>New Garden page</h1>
    <p>Enter the year for the garden year you wish to track.  You can also record a few notes, or update them as the year progresses.  For example, when did you start planting, when was the last freeze/frost date, what was the weather like that year. You can leave the Seed ID field empty for now (reserved for future functionality)</p>

    <form action="/gardens" method="POST">
        Seed ID: <input type="text" name="seedId"><br>
        Year: <input type="text" name="year"><br>
        Notes: <input type="text" name="notes" id="textArea"><br>
        <input type="submit" value="Create Garden">
    </form>

    <br>
    <nav>
        <a href='/seeds'>Back to Seeds page</a>
        <a href="/gardens/">View gardens</a>
    </nav>
</body>
